  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/413750/extras/ce153ce591590950fd512355e94e7ad1.avif?t=1580756799\" width=764 height=96 /></span><br><br><strong>Turtle VR</strong> brings the Logo turtle into the 21st century.  Use an interface similar to MIT Scratch, and Google Blockly, to program a turtle to draw your creations within various 3D worlds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/413750/extras/7eb58c3433bfadab5aac7aefd08267fc.avif?t=1580756799\" width=764 height=170 /></span><br><br>Using a tablet style interface, combined with Google’s Blockly, you are able to drive a programmable turtle in real-time while in VR. Draw and explore geometry using the code blocks Turtle VR provides, and browse through the provided catalog of programs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/413750/extras/a8944e659da849f74110c3a1473123e7.avif?t=1580756799\" width=764 height=126 /></span><br><br>Block-based programming makes it easy for anyone to get started.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/413750/extras/ce153ce591590950fd512355e94e7ad1.avif?t=1580756799\" width=764 height=96 /></span><br><br><strong>Turtle VR</strong> brings the Logo turtle into the 21st century.  Use an interface similar to MIT Scratch, and Google Blockly, to program a turtle to draw your creations within various 3D worlds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/413750/extras/7eb58c3433bfadab5aac7aefd08267fc.avif?t=1580756799\" width=764 height=170 /></span><br><br>Using a tablet style interface, combined with Google’s Blockly, you are able to drive a programmable turtle in real-time while in VR. Draw and explore geometry using the code blocks Turtle VR provides, and browse through the provided catalog of programs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/413750/extras/a8944e659da849f74110c3a1473123e7.avif?t=1580756799\" width=764 height=126 /></span><br><br>Block-based programming makes it easy for anyone to get started.",
